> <OLD>

> " Leo Prime, we will do everything in our power to help you but, before we
> can  do that, we have to fortify our energy reserves.  We can not succeed on
> what little we have.  Quickstride is the key to providing us with the
> resources we need to carry out a successful mission."

<NEW>

As TUSCON was talking LEO PRIME was looking down at something that
AIRHAMMER, who had just came in as TUSCON and his team were returning,
had handed to him.

Glancing back up at TUSCON, LEO PRIME nodded, "Agreed. Energy is
something that we will all need. Begin at once."

He glanced back down at the Padd and continued speaking, "Airhammer
just gave me a quick report on his mission to pick up Nighshift." LEO
looked back up at TUSCON, "Any word on Cheetor who is still missing?"

LEO PRIME glanced over at the green bot with the Predacon signature
and then back at TUSCON, "And this bot here tells me that some
criminals may have escaped from that ship that fell from the sky. Part
of Airhammer's report shows an individual floating above a massive
heard of Dinosaurs of all types."

Lowering the Padd, LEO's face took on a stern cast, "We may have more
to deal with then the Unicronians, the Predacons and leaving this
world untouched." He puased, looked at his padd, the green robot and
then back at TUSCON, "There are criminals that will have to be
recovered."

(TAG)

Preston
